Package com.hotelapplication.backend

Class Manager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hotelapplication.backend.User
      • com.hotelapplication.backend.Manager
  • public class Manager
extends User
    Represents a manager in the hotel reservation system. This class extends the User class and adds additional functionality specific to managers, including managing employee-specific details such as employee number, start date, and end date. It also includes methods to manage and print account information.
    Author:
    Alexander Boutselis
